      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MERCEDES BELLE (1) was speedy out of box 5 on debut to score by one length (19.87) at this track over 352m. Drawn to take advantage of good early pace. Should be in this for a long way. POOKIE BEAR (8) has missed the frame at her last two but did run well three back when second (19.97) in a Grade 6 at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from on outside draw. Has the ability and expected to do much better. STAINED ACES (2) missed the frame last time when fourth (16.89) at Q Straight but prior to that had two placings in a row. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Must be included in calculations. JAG THE JOKER (4) can sneak into the finish.",
